            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokémon Center]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pokémon Center TAIPEI]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1209303</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Pokémon Center TAIPEI 于今（8 日）在台湾<strong>新光三越</strong> 台北信义新天地 A11 3 楼<strong>开幕</strong> ，期间推出不少台湾特色例如夜市、水果为主题的限量商品。只要在开幕期间消费够指定金额，即可获得开幕纪念特典卡。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209307 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-694x461.png" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-694x461.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-1280x849.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-768x510.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM-1536x1019.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.07.01-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pokémon Center TAIPEI</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Pokémon Center TAIPEI 除了是台湾第一间 Pokémon Center 外，亦是非日本本土第二间 Pokémon Center，店面设计是以「天空与海洋环绕的风景」为灵感。店面会有启暴龙和比卡超塑像欢迎顾客。店内陈列多款 Pokémon 商品，而日后也会举办不同 Pokémon 相关活动。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209304 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-694x466.png" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-694x466.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-1280x860.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-768x516.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM-1536x1032.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.03.34-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Pokémon Center TAIPEI</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">是次开幕有数量总计达 29 款的开幕纪念商品，有 Pokémon Center TAIPEI Pokémon 悠游卡，纯金打造、以 Pokémon Center TAIPEI 标志设计，售价新台币 15 万元的纯金徽标，Pokémon Center TAIPEI 设计款比卡超、启暴龙等毛绒玩具，还有环保袋、附盖滤茶杯、橡胶挂绳、浴巾、纸胶带套组、侧开笔记本、徽标胸针、杯套、附盖环保吸管、贴纸套组、便当袋、茶壶、附拉链毛巾、垫子、箱型便利贴、A4 文件夹、餐垫餐具套组等商品。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209306 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-694x460.png" alt="" width="694" height="460" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-694x460.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-1280x848.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-768x509.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM-1536x1017.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-08-at-2.05.25-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲有数量总计达 29 款的开幕纪念商品</p><p>▲资料及图片来源：<a href="https://atctwn.com/2023/12/08/80297/">ATC</a>，<a href="https://news.gamebase.com.tw/news/detail/99417922">游戏基地</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

