                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">2023 年的香港车坛压轴登场：皇冠汽车为香港驾驶者带来 Toyota 首部纯电动车 ALL-NEW bZ4X；新车搭载 Toyota 纯电车专属的 eTNGA 底盘，拥有前衞外型及流线车身，同时提供宽敞的车箱空间。bZ4X 将于本周末（12 月 9 至 10 日）在沙田新城市广场及各大丰田陈列室登场！</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209493 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_153512-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Toyota ALL-NEW bZ4X</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>车身设计具科技感</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">「科技感」与「前衞」是 bZ4X 的代名词。车身外型设计稳健硬朗，有跑格的设计语调，车身线条流畅，低腰线贴近轮圈。 车头采用了锤头式设计并配置「4 眼」LED 头灯及一体式尾灯组合；车头顶部及两侧，车尾特有的左右独立尾翼均具空气力学扰流设计，降低风阻并提供更稳定的行车与续航表现，亦配备 20 吋合金轮圈，配合全黑色及 5 款双色车身。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209495 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516410-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209496 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151648-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209497 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151708-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209498 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151602-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209503 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1515560-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲车头采用了锤头式设计并配置「4 眼」LED 头灯及一体式尾灯组合</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>车里</strong><strong>空间</strong><strong>感舒服度高</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">bZ4X 的空间感与舒适度高；受惠于 eTNGA 底盘及 2,850mm 长轴距设计，前后排乘客距离有 1000mm；仪表板及车厢内多处以高级纤维织布包裹让驾乘者更感静谧。同时，全景天幕连电动幕帘让驾驶者的视野更开扬。标准配备前排冷暖通风座椅及双区域自动恒温冷气系统。车内多处收纳空间也尽得其用，加上 441 公升特大尾箱连脚控电尾门，两层底板灵活实用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209506 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151614-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209509 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151820-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲前后排乘客距离有 1000mm</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209508 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1516200-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲仪表板及车厢内多处以高级纤维织布包裹让驾乘者更感静谧</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>电池容量达 71.4 kWh 续航力达 436 公里</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">全轮驱动的 bZ4X 是首部搭载 eTNGA 纯电车型专属底盘的车款，设计上将行车电池装置在车底；底盘与电池一体化的设计，使 bZ4X 重心更低并且平均分配重量和位置，也提高车架刚性、操控性能及驾驶安全。厂方设计轻量化车身，亦让力量传递更精准。bZ4X 采用由丰田与 Panasonic 共同研发及制造的行车电池，容量 71.4kWh，具备电池冷却功能，续航力高达 436 公里。快速充电由 10%-80% 只需短短 30 分钟，全新的电能驱动系统，最大马力输出 203（150kW）、最大扭力达  266Nm。而 bZ4X 配备刹车动能回收系统，让驾驶者能够自由选择动能回收的时间。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209512 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151851-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲续航力高达 436 公里。快速充电由 10%-80% 只需短短 30 分钟</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">bZ4X 的娱乐配备和行车科技包括：7 吋全电子仪表及多功能显示屏、12.3 吋原厂轻触式屏幕音响系统连无线 Apple CarPlay 及原厂导航系统、原厂 JBL 高级音响系统连 9 个喇叭、Qi 电话无线充电装置、前排放射式加热系统、丰田首度采用的旋钮式排档等；其中 7 吋全电子仪表及多功能显示屏更是采用全新布局，从用家角度出发，驾驶时观看仪表更方便。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209507 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151624-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209510 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151831-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲7 吋全电子仪表及多功能显示屏更是采用全新布局，从用家角度出发，驾驶时观看仪表更方便</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209511 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_151836-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲丰田首度采用的旋钮式排档</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>新增了司机监测系统，独立镜头监测司机动态</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">bZ4X 配备第 3 代丰田主动式安全系统（Toyota Safety Sense™️3.0），首次新增了司机监测系统，以独立镜头监测司机动态，在可能发生潜在危险时作主动提醒。另外，升级的行车雷达及镜头，大大提升监察能力，使预警式防护系统可于更远的距离辅助驾驶者，甚至作自动刹车。bZ4X 也标准配置了 9 个安全气袋、8 个前后泊车警示器、泊车防碰撞辅助系统、原厂 360 度全景泊车影像系统等安全设备。bZ4X 更是香港首部丰田型号引入自动泊车辅助系统 （Advanced Park），不论 L 位或 S 位都可轻松解决泊车疑难。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209513 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-694x391.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="391" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-694x391.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-1280x721.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-1536x865.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/20231208_1519260-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲香港首部丰田型号引入自动泊车辅助系统 （Advanced Park）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><u>ALL-NEW bZ4X 售价：</u><u><br /></u>HK$ 349,860 （一换一后售价）</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;"><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

