                <![CDATA[<div><p><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">中国</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">电动车电池龙头企业宁德时代</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">与香港</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">科技园公司</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">签署</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">合作备忘录</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">，</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">并将在科学园</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">设立国际总部</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">及</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">研发中心</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1209213 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-8.10.49-PM-694x455.png" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-8.10.49-PM-694x455.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-8.10.49-PM-1280x838.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-8.10.49-PM-768x503.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-8.10.49-PM-1536x1006.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/Screenshot-2023-12-07-at-8.10.49-PM.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲<span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">中国</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">电动车电池龙头企业宁德时代</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">与香港</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">科技园公司</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">签署</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">合作备忘录</span></p></div><div><p><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">科技园公司行政总裁黄克强</span><span lang="ZH-TW" style="font-size: 16px;">表示，</span><span lan