        <item>
            <title>《GTA 6》未推出 PC 版，或因「双重购买」可赚更多</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/09/gta-6-no-pc-yet/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=gta-6-no-pc-yet</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/12/09/gta-6-no-pc-yet/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 09 Dec 2023 09:01:22 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[grand theft auto]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GTA 6]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[rockstar]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1208985</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>昨日 Rockstar 终于推出《GTA 6》官方预告片（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/05/gta6-2025-on-ps5-xbox-x-s/game-channel/">相关报道</a>），令不少玩家非常兴奋，不过可惜的是，游戏开发商的母公司 Take-Two 发布的官方新闻稿确认首发仅限主机平台，而 PC 版则仍是音讯杳然。游戏资讯网站 Playtracker.net 表示或因「双重购买」所以 Rockstar 尚未公布有关 PC 版本何时推出。</p><p>PlayTrack.net 在 X （前称 Twitter）上的帖文表示，有近半数（44%）《GTA 5》 玩家在多个平台均拥有该款游戏。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Why isn&#39;t <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/GTA6?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#GTA6</a> coming to PC yet? </p><p>According to our data, 44% of GTA V owners have the game on multiple platforms. The &quot;double dip&quot; is very real. <a href="https://t.co/ysxL7EV7Mz">pic.twitter.com/ysxL7EV7Mz</a></p><p>&mdash; PlayTracker (@PlayTrackerNet) <a href="https://twitter.com/PlayTrackerNet/status/1731985627149639774?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 5, 2023</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>据外媒 Game Debate 引述 PlayTracker 数据显示， 有近一半玩家多次购买了 GTA 5，意思是这些玩家在多个平台上均拥有 GTA 5 游戏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1208988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/id1543318238_343178-406x580.jpg" alt="" width="406" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/id1543318238_343178-406x580.jpg 406w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/id1543318238_343178-630x900.jpg 630w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/id1543318238_343178-768x1098.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/id1543318238_343178-1074x1536.jpg 1074w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/12/id1543318238_343178.jpg 1080w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 406px" /></p><p>由于《GTA 5》有近半数玩家会购买游戏一次以上，Take Two 可能食髓知味，暂时不公布 PC 版本推出日期也许是商业上的考虑。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/PlayTrackerNet/status/1731985627149639774">PlayTrackerNet@X</a>、<a href="https://www.game-debate.com/news/26026/45-of-grand-theft-auto-v-players-double-dipped-according-to-playtracker-data">Game Debate</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

